value:
The Management Measures tool allows users to search and query the Tethys Management Measures Tool for Marine Renewable Energy - a robust compilation of marine energy management measures identified by international Marine Renewable Energy regulators and researchers.
Source: [Management Measures Tool for Marine Renewable Energy | Tethys](https://tethys.pnnl.gov/management-measures)

The FERC eLibrary contains environmental compliance project documents, 
          of which excerpts have been manually tagged for reference.
The [Tethys Marine Energy Knowledge Base](https://tethys.pnnl.gov/knowledge-base-marine-energy) contains curated white and gray literature.
Spatial intersections are displayed here between the location drawn and datasets loaded from [MarineCadastre.gov](https://MarineCadastre.gov) of species, habitats and human uses as Receptor tags.
